title: Google\Cloud\Dataproc\V1\ManagedCluster
name: ManagedCluster
description:
Cluster that is managed by the workflow.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.dataproc.v1.ManagedCluster

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.cluster_name
params.description: Required. The cluster name prefix. A unique cluster name will be formed by appending a random suffix. The name must contain only lower-case letters (a-z), numbers (0-9), and hyphens (-). Must begin with a letter. Cannot begin or end with hyphen. Must consist of between 2 and 35 characters.

params.name: data.labels
params.description: Optional. The labels to associate with this cluster. Label keys must be between 1 and 63 characters long, and must conform to the following PCRE regular expression: [\p{Ll}\p{Lo}][\p{Ll}\p{Lo}\p{N}-]{0,62} Label values must be between 1 and 63 characters long, and must conform to the following PCRE regular expression: [\p{Ll}\p{Lo}\p{N}-]{0,63} No more than 32 labels can be associated with a given cluster.
